pr_body:
Major Features added:
- CNN/ANN network Policy designer tab
- Support for parallel multi-environment experimentation
- Implemented Tensorboard into the GUI
- Added training and testing plots, running on their separate threads
- Added progress bar and current status box to keep track of program
- Added Sokoban and LunarLander Environments
- Soft saving of trained model to its current scene
- Loading of GraphML flow files created in DHGWorkflow
